1. *Došao* sam kući kasno sinoć. (I came home late last night.)
2. On je već *došao* na sastanak. (He has already arrived at the meeting.)
3. Da li si *došao* sa nekim drugim? (Did you come with someone else?)
4. Kada budeš *došao*, pozovi me. (When you arrive, call me.)
5. Ona je *došla* da poseti svoju tetku. (She came to visit her aunt.)
6. Mi smo *došli* u ovaj grad pre tri dana. (We arrived in this city three days ago.)
7. Da li ćeš *doći* na moju proslavu rođendana? (Will you come to my birthday party?)
8. Oni *dolaze* za jedan sat. (They are coming in one hour.)
9. Kada *bude došao* lepši dan, idemo u park. (When a nicer day comes, we will go to the park.)
10. *Dolazim* sutra ujutru. (I am coming tomorrow morning.)